(As I wandered through a high-vaulted corridor deep within a mighty citad\el, I paused to admire the )Tj
T*
(magnificent architecture. )Tj
0 -2.55714 TD
(Somehow the contemplation of these majestic surroundings stimulated the \realization that I was )Tj
/T1_1 1 Tf
