T*
(powerful, it is first necessary to consider the way in which ordinary dr\eamers experience being in the )Tj
T*
(dream world. Non-lucid dreamers perceive themselves as being contained w\ithin the experiential world )Tj
T*
(of their dreams. Whether they play starring roles or are only pawns in t\he dream game, they are still )Tj
T*
