T*
(research, and that was that. Philosophers have also tended to find anecd\otes of lucid dreaming )Tj
T*
(problematic and even absurd, and this is one of the reasons that the mer\e existence of lucid dreams is )Tj
T*
(conceptually important. The proven fact of lucid dreaming effectively ch\allenges a number of )Tj
