T*
(want to reconcile or heal some division you feel within yourself. You mi\ght suffer from terrifying )Tj
T*
(nightmares and yearn to sleep peacefully, without fear; perhaps you feel\ lost, inadequate, or depressed\227)Tj
T*
(or simply curious to explore the adventures of the dream world. )Tj
0 -2.55714 TD
