T*
(particular dream events, thus allowing for the convenient testing of oth\erwise untestable hypotheses. A )Tj
T*
(researcher can ask a subject to perform any chosen action within the dre\am, and the lucid dreamer can )Tj
T*
(carry these directions out. This signaling also allows a clear mapping o\f mind/body relationships. )Tj
0 -2.55714 TD
