(Take a few minutes, now, to observe your present state of awareness. Fir\st of all, notice the richly varied )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(and vivid impressions harvested by your visual sense alone\227shapes, co\lors, movement, dimensionality. )Tj
T*
(Next, register the various sounds taken in by your ears\227a diverse ran\ge of intensities, pitches, and tonal )Tj
T*
(qualities, perhaps including the commonplace miracle of speech or the wo\nder of music. Observe the )Tj
T*
