(land. You shall seek and find and bring back a precious Jewel.' )Tj
0 -2.55714 TD
(The travellers were conducted in disguise to a strange land, whose inhab\itants almost all )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(lived a dark existence. Such was the effect of this place that the two l\ost touch with each )Tj
